articles.title: Lights out for wonky US lunar lander, for now - Space Daily
articles.description: Washington (AFP) March 1, 2024 -  An uncrewed American lander that became the first private spaceship on the Moon sent its final image Thursday before its power banks depleted, the company that built it said.
